snippet.title: True Crime Brewery
snippet.description: Tiegrabber Podcasts produces True Crime Brewery, a true crime podcast unlike any other!  Husband and wife, Jill and Dick, use their medical knowledge and life experiences to take a deep dive into some of the most fascinating crimes from all over the world.  Just for fun, Dick uses his expertise as a craft beer lover to review and/or recommend beers from the regions where each crime occurred.  Meet them at the quiet end of the bar for a craft brew and a no-holds-barred true crime discussion.
